lead_paragraph: Paris St Germain striker Edinson Cavani wasted enough chances to win four football matches in his side's two Champions League clashes against Arsenal but remained upbeat after a 2-2 draw on Wednesday put his side in pole position in Group A.

headline.print_headline: PSG Passed a Test, Says Wasteful Cavani
headline.main: PSG Passed a Test, Says Wasteful Cavani
